##### tag

    ~ medusa-tag a-file some tags

Creates links:

    ~/.medusa/some/a-file
    ~/.medusa/tags/a-file

```
location <- pwd name
mapM (link name) tags
  where link name tag = writeFile (tagPath name tag) location
        tagPath name tag = "~/.medusa/" ++ tag ++ "/" ++ name
```

##### archive

    ~ medusa-archive a-file

Removes all the tags except `archive`

